title: Pampers Preemie Swaddlers: A Touch Of Love | Diapers for Premature Babies
description:
Introducing Pampers’ smallest diaper ever, because #TouchesOfLove are important to a premature baby. Pampers Swaddlers is the #1 choice of hospitals*, and our preemie diapers are designed with NICU nurses to wrap babies in a loving touch.

Under the Pampers Touches of Love campaign this fall, we’ve joined forces with the March of Dimes, the only national organization dedicated to finding the causes of preterm birth. Together, we’ll celebrate all babies, especially the ones in the NICU, and those who care for them. Starting today through World Prematurity Day (November 17), we are inviting everyone to celebrate babies by sharing pictures of your baby’s #touchesoflove moments with @Pampers on Twitter & Facebook and @PampersUS on Instagram. For every post using #touchesoflove, we’ll make a $1 donation to the March of Dimes.** 

Pampers Preemie Swaddlers, our smallest diapers ever, are designed for premature babies.

transcripts: Here's a little touch my darling, a little souvenir. "Hi baby." Something to keep with you even when I can't be near. Let it wrap you in it's calm like the warm summer air. Let it show you that your loved much more than you are aware. "I miss you beauty." A touch of love that's what I leave with you. For a tender loving patch, will last the whole night through. Pampers believes every touch of love matters for a premature baby, That's why we are introducing out smallest diaper ever designed with NICU nurses to wrap the tiniest premature babies in a gentle loving touch. Pampers swaddlers the number one choice of hospitals. Wishing you love, sleep, and play.
